==================================================
PHASE 07.5 GOAL
==================================================

Implement REALTIME DASHBOARD STREAMING.

Add:
- backend websocket streaming layer
- frontend realtime hooks
- live risk updates
- live scheduler updates
- live content pipeline updates
- live event feed
- reconnect-safe websocket client
- heartbeat/ping support
- dashboard live status indicators

This phase upgrades the dashboard from polling-only
to realtime streaming architecture.

==================================================
REQUIRED ARCHITECTURE
==================================================

BACKEND
--------
FastAPI websocket gateway:

  /ws/events
  /ws/risk
  /ws/scheduler
  /ws/content

Frontend:
- one shared realtime client layer
- auto reconnect
- exponential backoff
- heartbeat detection
- stale connection recovery
- typed event envelopes

Streaming events must support:
- risk alerts
- halt state changes
- guardian events
- scheduler runs
- scheduler failures
- content pipeline status
- approval state changes
- system notifications
- mock/live mode indicators

==================================================
BACKEND IMPLEMENTATION
==================================================

Create/update:

backend/app/realtime/
  __init__.py
  manager.py
  events.py
  schemas.py
  broadcaster.py
  heartbeat.py

backend/app/api/realtime.py

Integrate with:
- risk guardian
- scheduler service
- content pipeline
- event logger
- dashboard metrics

==================================================
REQUIRED BACKEND FEATURES
==================================================

1. Connection manager
- track clients
- track channels
- graceful disconnects
- cleanup dead sockets

2. Typed event envelopes

Example:

{
  "type": "risk.alert",
  "timestamp": "...",
  "source": "guardian",
  "severity": "warning",
  "payload": {...}
}

3. Broadcast helpers

Examples:
- broadcast_risk_alert()
- broadcast_scheduler_run()
- broadcast_content_update()
- broadcast_system_status()

4. Heartbeat
- ping/pong
- stale timeout cleanup
- safe disconnect handling

5. Safety
- no trading execution
- no broker routing
- no live order control
- streaming is informational only

