==================================================
VALIDATION REQUIREMENTS
==================================================

ALL MUST PASS:

Backend:
  cd backend
  source .venv/bin/activate
  python -m ruff check app tests
  python -B -m pytest -q

Frontend:
  cd frontend
  source ~/.nvm/nvm.sh
  nvm use 20
  npm test
  npm run build

Optional:
  docker build -f infra/docker/backend.Dockerfile .
  docker build -f infra/docker/frontend.Dockerfile .

==================================================
SAFETY REQUIREMENTS
==================================================

- realtime layer MUST remain informational only
- no live trading enablement
- no bypass of guardian protections
- no direct broker communication
- no unsafe websocket commands
- websocket payloads must be validated
- heartbeat failures must safely disconnect
- reconnect loops must be rate-limited

==================================================
EXPECTED OUTCOME
==================================================

After implementation:

- dashboard updates live without refresh
- risk alerts appear instantly
- scheduler jobs stream live state
- content approvals update live
- websocket reconnect works safely
- stale connections recover automatically
- frontend tests remain green
- backend tests remain green
- build remains production-safe

